---
title: Beef Kofta Tray Bake with Couscous and Lemony Hummus Sauce
description: 2022 is the year of the tray bake! Layers of zucchini, peppers and shawarma-spiced kofta get baked to perfection, then piled on top of pearl couscous and finished with lemony garlic-hummus sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-kofta-tray-bake-a88b47b8.jpg
